fine-tuning of WAN2.2-TI2V-5B for surgical video generation.

This project builds on, and is intended to be used together with, the
following third-party works, each governed by its own license:

  - WAN2.2 / Wan2.1 video model and backbone code (the `wan` package)
    https://github.com/Wan-Video
